{"tid":1494327,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支那01]余若薇投訴何君堯　律師會：不公開調查進展及結果","createTime":"2019-08-21T15:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T01:14:01.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05284a065948bd1e09e443d0e45d464019981480","tid":1494327,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3187700/org/90fc004c8eff53121ceb3d2cb049d5b8.jpg/nt97ek7WNcg2n5H6UmuWb_XMaoQX9tqBMGW_UDBlv1A?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3187700%2Forg%2F90fc004c8eff53121ceb3d2cb049d5b8.jpg%2Fnt97ek7WNcg2n5H6UmuWb_XMaoQX9tqBMGW_UDBlv1A%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=08e0d9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3186890/org/ea9d87a839a28f0e453fbc8688580dee.jpg/g8AzHBJE_40rIf3kls-t0bGMeyW1x3u_lDLhQJQy4UA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3186890%2Forg%2Fea9d87a839a28f0e453fbc8688580dee.jpg%2Fg8AzHBJE_40rIf3kls-t0bGMeyW1x3u_lDLhQJQy4UA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1de82e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余若薇早前向律師會投訴，指何君堯懷疑與毆打事件有關聯，涉嫌違反《律師執業規則》。律師會隨後證實已接個案，正嚴正檢視有關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n律師會今發出通知，指律師會經審查後，將以投訴人的身份接手由公眾人士（即「舉報人士」）提出的針對何君堯的投訴，並表示「由於所有專業調查均屬保密，舉報人將不會被告之調查進展及結果」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3186848/org/f08b8ca7302aaa672a7d5722562cd5ff.jpg/4oYMckrkzzbisSJfxmd_nujTogzCgNwMfMAbb3zAG28?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3186848%2Forg%2Ff08b8ca7302aaa672a7d5722562cd5ff.jpg%2F4oYMckrkzzbisSJfxmd_nujTogzCgNwMfMAbb3zAG28%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=248c1f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃鶴鳴指，以往律師會只會處理投訴，而較少越俎代庖成為投訴人，因為律師會既作為監管機構，又作為投訴人，會令人感到有角色衝突，而且因投訴屬具名，律師會毋須接手，此舉會令律師會處於尷尬地位。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他又指律師會以往會向投訴人交代處理投訴結果，今次決定不公開，質疑不符慣例，「令人擔心是否唔想話畀人聽」，加上何君堯屬公眾人物，社會對其言行有期望，亦會影響社會對律師的觀感，故認為律師會有責任交代結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/366456/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95%E5%8F%8A%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama&amp;fbclid=IwAR2zAYuuDLBaK-yARwj1tMAW8_kaY0-RoTrzLofKfR6z-xtFHCh8HJwCDT0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F366456%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E4%25BD%2599%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2596%2587%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama%26fbclid%3DIwAR2zAYuuDLBaK-yARwj1tMAW8_kaY0-RoTrzLofKfR6z-xtFHCh8HJwCDT0&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn0wz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=4a22783b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/366456/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95%E5%8F%8A%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama&amp;fbclid=IwAR2zAYuuDLBaK-yARwj1tMAW8_kaY0-RoTrzLofKfR6z-xtFHCh8HJwCDT0</a>"},{"pid":"f42b0402476bfb29afef377531c088ff5adff8c5","tid":1494327,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:56:26.000Z","msg":"我都收到咁既回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7b3eb459fb864a4f322d98345c123089c1de96","tid":1494327,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0